Germany’s Lindner Expects FDP Member Vote on ESM, Hamburger Says

-- B y   N a o m i   K r e s g e
-- 
2011-09-17T10:02:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-17/germany-s-lindner-expects-fdp-member-vote-on-esm-hamburger-says.html
German Chancellor  Angela Merkel ’s
Free Democratic Party coalition partner is likely to hold a vote
on members’ attitude toward the European Stability Mechanism,
the permanent euro rescue fund, newspaper  Hamburger Abendblatt 
cited FDP General Secretary Christian Lindner as saying in an
interview.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Naomi Kresge in Berlin at 
